---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'IMG Global Review', href: '/providers/img-global' },
  { title: 'GeoBlue Review', href: '/providers/geoblue' },
  { title: 'Best US Expat Insurance', href: '/best/us-expat-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'img', header: 'IMG Global' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', img: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', img: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', img: 'Limited', geoblue: 'Moderate' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', img: '12 mo wait', geoblue: '12 mo wait' },
  { feature: 'Dental', img: 'Optional', geoblue: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', img: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', img: true, geoblue: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', img: 'Included (most plans)', geoblue: 'Included (BCBS)' },
  { feature: 'High Deductible Options', img: 'Up to $25,000', geoblue: 'Up to $5,000' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'age', header: 'Age' },
  { key: 'img', header: 'IMG Global' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { age: '30', img: '$120-200/mo', geoblue: '$150-230/mo' },
  { age: '40', img: '$160-280/mo', geoblue: '$200-310/mo' },
  { age: '50', img: '$220-360/mo', geoblue: '$280-430/mo' },
  { age: '60', img: '$340-520/mo', geoblue: '$400-620/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="IMG Global vs GeoBlue"
  description="Compare IMG Global and GeoBlue international health insurance. Value flexibility vs BCBS network access for US expats."
  headline="IMG Global vs GeoBlue"
  subheadline="Two US-based options with different approaches. Flexibility vs network access."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    IMG Global and GeoBlue are both US-based international health insurers popular with American expats. IMG offers flexibility and value; GeoBlue provides BCBS network integration.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">IMG Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Lower premiums overall</li>
        <li>Highly customizable plans</li>
        <li>Very high deductible options</li>
        <li>Good for healthy individuals</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">GeoBlue</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>BCBS network (1.7M+ providers)</li>
        <li>Seamless US coverage</li>
        <li>Better mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Stronger brand recognition</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get quotes from IMG and GeoBlue."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both include US coverage by default. The main differences are network access and plan flexibility.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Key differences:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>GeoBlue has BCBS network access; IMG uses broader but less integrated networks</li>
    <li>IMG offers much higher deductible options (up to $25K vs $5K)</li>
    <li>GeoBlue has better mental health coverage</li>
    <li>IMG is more customizable overall</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    IMG is typically 15-25% cheaper than GeoBlue for similar coverage. The gap widens with high-deductible strategies.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Pricing notes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>IMG's high-deductible plans can be 40%+ cheaper</li>
    <li>GeoBlue's BCBS access may justify premium for frequent US users</li>
    <li>Both include US coverage in these estimates</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>IMG Global</strong> works with various networks globally. US coverage is included but without guaranteed BCBS rates.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>GeoBlue</strong> provides direct BCBS network access—negotiated rates at 90% of US hospitals and 1.7M+ providers.
  </p>

  <h3>Claims Process</h3>
  <p>
    Both offer online claims. GeoBlue's BCBS integration means simpler direct billing in the US. IMG may require more reimbursement claims.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose IMG Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Budget is a primary concern</li>
        <li>You want high-deductible options</li>
        <li>You rarely use US healthcare</li>
        <li>You're healthy and want catastrophic coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose GeoBlue If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You visit the US frequently</li>
        <li>You want BCBS network rates</li>
        <li>Mental health coverage matters</li>
        <li>You prefer established brand backing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    For budget-conscious expats who rarely return to the US, IMG Global offers better value with more flexibility. The high-deductible options make it especially attractive for healthy individuals.
  </p>
  <p>
    For expats who regularly visit the US or want the security of BCBS network access, GeoBlue justifies its premium. The seamless US integration is worth paying for if you'll use it.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Get quotes from both providers."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage details change. Verify all information with providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
